class.name: Activities
class.abstract: The collection of activities related to the current activity.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: This method gets the specified activity on the current activities management.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: This method removes the specified activity on the current activities management.

class.abstract: The object that represents an activity.

method.name: AddAttr
method.abstract: Adds attribute to an Activity.

method.name: AttrName
method.abstract: This method returns the name for the specified attribute.

method.name: AttrValue
method.abstract: This method returns the value for the specified attribute.

method.abstract: This method creates a new child activity of the requested type.

method.name: CreateLink
method.abstract: This method creates a link from the current activity to another activity.

method.abstract: This method removes a link existing on the current activity.

method.abstract: This property returns the number of attributes of the current activity.

method.name: CalculatedBeginTime
